  Dialogue:
  - DialogueText: Hello, how's the work going?
    TypingSpeed: 0.02
    StartColor: {r: 0, g: 0, b: 0, a: 0}
    EndColor: {r: 0.8207547, g: 0.8207547, b: 0.8207547, a: 1}
    ColorCurve:
      serializedVersion: 2
      m_Curve:
      - serializedVersion: 3
        time: 0
        value: 0
        inSlope: 2
        outSlope: 2
        tangentMode: 0
        weightedMode: 0
        inWeight: 0
        outWeight: 0
      - serializedVersion: 3
        time: 1
        value: 1
        inSlope: 0
        outSlope: 0
        tangentMode: 0
        weightedMode: 0
        inWeight: 0
        outWeight: 0
      m_PreInfinity: 2
      m_PostInfinity: 2
      m_RotationOrder: 4
  - DialogueText: There's not much said about elves in the books and news, so they
      are trying to fool guards at the checkpoints very often.
    TypingSpeed: 0.02
    StartColor: {r: 0, g: 0, b: 0, a: 0}
    EndColor: {r: 0.8207547, g: 0.8207547, b: 0.8207547, a: 1}
    ColorCurve:
      serializedVersion: 2
      m_Curve:
      - serializedVersion: 3
        time: 0
        value: 0
        inSlope: 2
        outSlope: 2
        tangentMode: 0
        weightedMode: 0
        inWeight: 0
        outWeight: 0
      - serializedVersion: 3
        time: 1
        value: 1
        inSlope: 0
        outSlope: 0
        tangentMode: 0
        weightedMode: 0
        inWeight: 0
        outWeight: 0
      m_PreInfinity: 2
      m_PostInfinity: 2
      m_RotationOrder: 4
  - DialogueText: Remember to only let them through if they are at least 150 years
      old.
    TypingSpeed: 0.02
    StartColor: {r: 0, g: 0, b: 0, a: 0}
    EndColor: {r: 0.8207547, g: 0.8207547, b: 0.8207547, a: 1}
    ColorCurve:
      serializedVersion: 2
      m_Curve:
      - serializedVersion: 3
        time: 0
        value: 0
        inSlope: 2
        outSlope: 2
        tangentMode: 0
        weightedMode: 0
        inWeight: 0
        outWeight: 0
      - serializedVersion: 3
        time: 1
        value: 1
        inSlope: 0
        outSlope: 0
        tangentMode: 0
        weightedMode: 0
        inWeight: 0
        outWeight: 0
      m_PreInfinity: 2
      m_PostInfinity: 2
      m_RotationOrder: 4
  - DialogueText: I don't think elves can ever reach the real MAN age, but let there
      be an exception.
    TypingSpeed: 0.02
    StartColor: {r: 0, g: 0, b: 0, a: 0}
    EndColor: {r: 0.8207547, g: 0.8207547, b: 0.8207547, a: 1}
    ColorCurve:
      serializedVersion: 2
      m_Curve:
      - serializedVersion: 3
        time: 0
        value: 0
        inSlope: 2
        outSlope: 2
        tangentMode: 0
        weightedMode: 0
        inWeight: 0
        outWeight: 0
      - serializedVersion: 3
        time: 1
        value: 1
        inSlope: 0
        outSlope: 0
        tangentMode: 0
        weightedMode: 0
        inWeight: 0
        outWeight: 0
      m_PreInfinity: 2
      m_PostInfinity: 2
      m_RotationOrder: 4
  - DialogueText: That's all for today, have a good shift.
    TypingSpeed: 0.02
    StartColor: {r: 0, g: 0, b: 0, a: 0}
    EndColor: {r: 0.8207547, g: 0.8207547, b: 0.8207547, a: 1}
